room_title: Escape room "Going Viral" by Escape 60 Peoria in Peoria
room_address: 931 N Sheridan Rd Suite B Peoria, IL 61606
room_description:
Dr. Stephanie Woods stumbled across a deadly air-born virus while working for DARKE pharmaceutical company. She desperately wanted to destroy it, fearing devastating consequences to the population but DARKE forced experimentation to continue. Now, Dr. Woods has gone missing.
While the police are out looking for the good doctor, it is your job to follow through on the message Dr. Woods left behind for you. You are her lab assistants and the only ones she trusts!
You must find the hidden virus and get out within the hour before DARKE agents get there first! If you donâ€™t get the virus out in time, DARKE will have access to the deadliest weapon humanity has ever known. The fate of millions is in your hands. Good luck!
